    "description": "An experiment has gone wrong, and the whole complex is failing. Your only chance at survival is to use the various tools at your disposal to escape this now-hostile environment. But beware: <i>an unrelenting force lurks in the shadows…</i><br><br>Play as Priya Ellis, a scientist whose research team has been decimated by a mysterious new form of life - the <i>Dark Matter</i> - which is <strong>invisible to the naked eye</strong>. Thanks to your <strong>scanner tablet</strong> and the ships' built-in <strong>surveillance system</strong>, you can <strong>outsmart the roaming menace</strong> by carefully <strong>planning your next move</strong>. But, keep an eye on <strong>your scanner’s energy</strong>: an empty battery would only guarantee your demise! <strong>Locking the doors</strong> behind you and <strong>luring the <i>Dark Matter</i></strong> to energy sources comes at a high risk, <i>but it could buy you some time… </i><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore a Hi-Tech environment!</strong></h2>Climb aboard the spaceship, and discover a state-of-the-art facility! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/dd35efff70c04437255cee63c4209749.poster.avif?t=1698691031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/dd35efff70c04437255cee63c4209749.webm?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/dd35efff70c04437255cee63c4209749.mp4?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenge the unknown, fight the darkness!</strong></h2>Come face-to-face with an unseen menace; push back the obscurity with your wits! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/e5a3f5a67c45b9b49764709ccdd35c56.poster.avif?t=1698691031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/e5a3f5a67c45b9b49764709ccdd35c56.webm?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/e5a3f5a67c45b9b49764709ccdd35c56.mp4?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Observe, Plan &amp; Execute!</strong></h2>Familiarize yourself with your surroundings, develop a strategy, and put your plan into action! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/0f8706ce16650f0db712279cfd89dca5.poster.avif?t=1698691031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/0f8706ce16650f0db712279cfd89dca5.webm?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/0f8706ce16650f0db712279cfd89dca5.mp4?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Investigate the events &amp; uncover the truth!</strong></h2>Figure out what happened onboard, and discover the true motivations of Anabasis &amp; Co.! <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/62ff588bb54109e5ddb16d29f49840ce.poster.avif?t=1698691031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480/extras/62ff588bb54109e5ddb16d29f49840ce.webm?t=1698691031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290480